The paper discusses monitoring distributed systems, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses modeling and detecting bugs, which falls under the category of Programming Languages (cs.PL) and Software Engineering (cs.SE). The paper uses Satisfiability Modulo Theories (SMT) solvers, which falls under the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
